com.fasterxml.jackson.jr.stree

Class JacksonJrsTreeCodec

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.fasterxml.jackson.core.TreeCodec
      • com.fasterxml.jackson.jr.stree.JacksonJrsTreeCodec

  • public class JacksonJrsTreeCodec
extends TreeCodec
    TreeCodec implementation that can build "simple", immutable (read-only) trees out of JSON: these are represented as subtypes of JrsValue ("Jrs" from "jackson JR Simple").
